Error message: 'pip' is not recognized as an internal or external command, operable program or batch file.
Solution: 
1) Right click on This PC
2) Go to Advanced System Settings
3) Environment Variables
4) Path
5) Edit
6) New
7) Here you need to add two paths: 1) the path where the python interpreter was installed (NOT PYCHARM) and 2) the python Scripts in the installation location.
